    <beast name="Air Elemental">
        <information>
            <type>Elemental</type>
            <demeanor>Selfish</demeanor>

            <origin>Harn</origin>
            <genre>Fantasy</genre>
        </information>

        <description>
            <short>
                A swirling column of air. Summoned with Lyhavi magic.
            </short>

            <physical>
                <para>
                    Air elementals are the largest of any of the elementals,
                    reaching titanic proportions. However, they are as
                    insubstantial as the element they are made from. They
                    consist of a whirling mass of air and whatever else they
                    can whip up - normally dust.
                </para>

                <para>
                    The larger elementals are towering dark tornados 30m
                    tall. They may reform themselves at will, though the
                    air they consist of is continuously moving.
                </para>

