                    columns of living fire, sprouting limbs of flame
                    capable of burning anything in their path.
                </para>

                <para>
                    A fire elemental is bright, noisy and not at all subtle.
                    They will try and burn anything they come into contact
                    with, though fires started in this way do not become
                    part of the elemental.
